INSERT INTO `structural_steel_work_collections` VALUES (1,'cjfdacxxav0yhdln836kgy1z','Hong Kong International Airport Contract 3501- Antenna Farm and Sewage Pumping Station','Hong Kong International Airport Contract 3501- Antenna Farm and Sewage Pumping Station','Hong Kong Airport Authority','12 June 2017 - 09 August 2018','<p>HKAA is required to relocate the existing antenna farm and one of the existing sewage pumping stations to facilitate the future expansion of Terminal 2.  This project includes the construction of the new antenna farm and sewage pumping station including associated utilities, road works and landscaping.</p><p>The works mainly comprise an antenna farm (including an antenna common equipment building and antenna tower) – complete with ABWF and building services; A sewage pumping station (Pumping</p><p>Station PS 12) – civil and structural engineering works only; Associated airport systems; Associated incoming and outgoing foul and grey water pipes; Associated roadworks, utilities, earth retaining walls and landscaping; Trenchless excavation for sewage rising mains; Associated testing and commissioning works; and All Temporary Works.</p>','2025-05-31 04:20:36.722000','2025-07-07 08:01:13.898000',NULL,8,36,'en'),(3,'dfw2xl7e1mwjqpa5pobexe1y','香港国际机场 合约编号3501 - 天线设备区及汙水抽水站工程','香港国际机场 合约编号3501 - 天线设备区及汙水抽水站工程','香港机场管理局','2017 年 06 月 12 日 - 2018 年 08 月 09 日','<p>香港机场管理局(HKAA)需要重置现有天线场和其中一个现有汙水泵站,以配合日后扩建二号客运大楼。本项目包括建设新的天线场和汙水抽水站，包括相关的公用设施、道路工程和景观工程。</p><p>主要工程包括天线场 (天线共用设备楼和天线塔) - 基本装修和建筑工程；汙水泵站(PS 12号泵站) - 包括土木和结构工程；相关机场系统；相关的进出汙水和灰水管道；相关道路工程、公用设施、挡土牆和景观工程；汙水输送主管使用无开挖方式建造；相关测试及调试工作和所有临时工程。</p>','2025-05-31 04:21:20.097000','2025-07-07 08:01:07.262000',NULL,8,36,'zh-CN'),(5,'rw9lxa5lbvhbljd79snrpqu4','香港國際機場 合約編號3501 - 天線設備區及污水抽水站工程','香港國際機場 合約編號3501 - 天線設備區及污水抽水站工程','香港機場管理局','2017 年 06 月 12 日 - 2018 年 08 月 09 日','<p>香港機場管理局(HKAA)需要重置現有天線場和其中一個現有污水泵站,以配合日後擴建二號客運大樓。本項目包括建設新的天線場和污水抽水站，包括相關的公用設施、道路工程和景觀工程。</p><p>主要工程包括天線場 (天線共用設備樓和天線塔) - 基本裝修和建築工程；污水泵站(PS 12號泵站) - 包括土木和結構工程；相關機場系統；相關的進出污水和灰水管道；相關道路工程、公用設施、擋土牆和景觀工程；污水輸送主管使用無開挖方式建造；相關測試及調試工作和所有臨時工程。</p>','2025-05-31 04:22:08.226000','2025-07-07 08:01:04.714000',NULL,8,36,'zh-Hant-HK'),(7,'oea41sxb6lnx6dzlkxgk68o1','合約編號HY/2016/04 將軍澳唐明街與唐德街之間的高架行人道','合約編號HY/2016/04 將軍澳唐明街與唐德街之間的高架行人道','路政署','2016 年 12 月 30 日 - 2021 年 03 月 03 日','<p>此工程主要目的是興建一條高架行人道，連接現時橫跨唐明街的行人天橋至港鐵將軍澳站上蓋之商場及在高架行人道近唐德街建造一部升降機以提供一條舒適和便捷的通道，方便將軍澳市中心一帶的居民(特別是長者)往來。此外，為增加區内可供居民使用的單車泊位數量，進行唐明街現有單車停泊處的重建及擴建工程。興建一條長約一百八十米、淨闊度約五米的高架行人道，連接現時橫跨唐明街的行人天橋至港鐵將軍澳站上蓋之商場；在擬議高架行人道近唐德街建造一部升降機； 重建及擴建現有單車停泊處；以及進行附屬工程，包括相關的道路、渠務、公用設施、公共照明、環境美化、機電系統等工程。</p>','2025-05-31 04:22:51.307000','2025-07-07 08:01:04.693000',NULL,8,36,'zh-Hant-HK'),(9,'fm0kclnrf2zckl2mavg39xbr','合约编号HY/2016/04 将军澳唐明街与唐德街之间的高架行人道','合约编号HY/2016/04 将军澳唐明街与唐德街之间的高架行人道','路政署','2016 年 12 月 30 日 - 2021 年 03 月 03 日','<p>此工程主要目的是兴建一条高 架行人道，连接现时横跨唐明街的行人天桥至港铁将军澳站上盖之商场及在高架行人道近唐德街建造一部升降机以提供一条舒适和便捷的通道，方便将军澳市中心一带的居民（特别是长者）往来。 此外，为增加区内可供居民使用的单车泊位数量，进行唐明街现有单车停泊处的重建及扩建工程。 兴建一条长约180米、净阔度约五米的高架行人道，连接现时横跨唐明街的行人天桥至港铁将军澳站上盖之商场;在拟议高架行人道近唐德街建造一部升降机; 重建及扩建现有单车停泊处;以及进行附属工程，包括相关的道路、渠务、公用设施、公共照明、环境美化、机电系统等工程。</p><br/><br/>','2025-05-31 04:23:26.551000','2025-07-07 08:01:10.655000',NULL,8,36,'zh-CN'),(11,'qiyytb7vitbw5ql9jwkitrjy','Contract No. HY/2016/04 Elevated Walkway between Tong Ming Street and Tong Tak Street , Tseung Kwan O','Contract No. HY/2016/04 Elevated Walkway between Tong Ming Street and Tong Tak Street , Tseung Kwan O','Highways Department','30 December 2016 - 03 March 2021','<p>The main purpose of this project is to construct an elevated walkway connecting the existing footbridge across Tong Ming Street to the shopping mall above Tseung Kwan O MTR Station and a lift at the end of the elevated walkway near Tong Tak Street to provide a comfortable and convenient access for residents (especially the elderly) of Tseung Kwan O town centre. The existing cycle parking area at Tong Ming Street is to be reconstructed and expanded to increase the number of cycle parking spaces for use by the residents of the area.</p><br/><p>This contract mainly comprises construction of an elevated walkway of about 180 m in length and about 5 m in clear width, connecting the existing footbridge across Tong Ming Street to the shopping mall above Tseung Kwan O MTR Station; construction of a lift at the end of the proposed elevated walkway near Tong Tak Street; reconstruction and expansion of the existing cycle parking area; and ancillary works, including associated road, drainage, public utilities, public lighting, landscaping, and electrical and mechanical works.</p>','2025-05-31 04:24:10.500000','2025-07-07 08:01:16.195000',NULL,8,36,'en'),(13,'xu3jo3jxbuby0l9tj8uxsh0k','The Hong Kong Polytechnic University Design and Build Contract for Footbridge Linking Phase 8 Development','The Hong Kong Polytechnic University Design and Build Contract for Footbridge Linking Phase 8 Development','The Hong Kong Polytechnic University','15 June 2015 - 29 August 2019','<p>The major scope of this project comprises the design and construction of a footbridge linking the Main Campus and the Phase 8 development of The Hong Kong Polytechnic University. The footbridge is designed as a steel bow-string arch structure with a main span length of 68m across the entire Chatham Road South. The pedestrian walkway with an overall width of about 7m and its associated sub-structures are hung from the two main arch beams by high-tensioned steel bar. The aesthetic form of the footbridge is designed according to the concept of &quot;Flying Fish&quot; and echoes with the surrounding iconic buildings of the University.</p><p>The works under the project include the design and construction of pile foundation, pile cap, RC lift shaft structures, lift installation, steel footbridge structure and its associated sub- structures, architectural works and finishes, building services works, footbridge connection works involving alternation and addition works to the existing Block Z at Phase 8 development.</p>','2025-05-31 04:25:33.348000','2025-07-07 08:01:14.130000',NULL,8,36,'en'),(15,'d5q0yf0hpjjyd7ubecreprf1','香港理工大学-设计及建造合约连接第八期校舍的行人天桥计划','香港理工大学-设计及建造合约连接第八期校舍的行人天桥计划','香港理工大学','2015 年 06 月 15 日 - 2019 年 08 月 29 日','<p>工程主要包括设计和建造连接香港理工大学主校园和第八期校舍的行人天桥。</p><p>主跨度为68米的钢管弓弦结构行人天桥位于漆咸道南。行人道整个宽度约7米而其附属结构由高拉钢悬挂在两个主拱梁上。此行人天桥的美学是根据&quot;飞鱼&quot;概念设计，与周围的标志性建筑互相呼应。</p><p>工程项目包括设计及建造桩地基，桩帽，钢筋混凝土升降机井结构，安装升降机，钢质行人天桥结构及其相关的附属结构，装饰及饰面，楼宇设备，涉及现有的Z座八期的交替及附加的工程的行人天桥连接工程。</p>','2025-05-31 04:26:15.127000','2025-07-07 08:01:11.505000',NULL,8,36,'zh-CN'),(17,'x0ke6lv76jx4efsj6juqd84o','香港理工大學-設計及建造合約連接第八期校舍的行人天橋計劃','香港理工大學-設計及建造合約連接第八期校舍的行人天橋計劃','香港理工大學','2015 年 06 月 15 日 - 2019 年 08 月 29 日','<p>工程主要包括設計和建造連接香港理工大學主校園和第八期校舍的行人天橋。</p><p>主跨度為68米的鋼管弓弦結構行人天橋位於漆咸道南。行人道整個寬度約7米而其附屬結構由高拉鋼懸掛在兩個主拱樑上。此行人天橋的美學是根據“飛魚”概念設計，與周圍的標誌性建築互相呼應。</p><p>工程項目包括設計及建造樁地基，樁帽，鋼筋混凝土升降機井結構，安裝升降機，鋼質行人天橋結構及其相關的附屬結構，裝飾及飾面，樓宇設備，涉及現有的Z座八期的交替及附加的工程的行人天橋連接工程。</p>','2025-05-31 04:26:50.766000','2025-07-07 08:01:04.758000',NULL,8,36,'zh-Hant-HK'),(19,'rsu1c811wpfcpla35atymje8','香港商用航空中心二號停機庫擴建工程(稱為三號停機庫)','香港商用航空中心二號停機庫擴建工程(稱為三號停機庫)','香港商用航空中心','2011 年 05 月 14 日 - 2012 年 05 月 31 日','<p>此工程是香港商用航空中心二號停機庫的擴建工程，座落於二號停機庫旁,稱為三號停機庫。新的三號停機庫與現有的停機庫相得益彰，提供足夠的機庫空間以滿足香港飛機庫不斷增長的需求。</p><p>此工程主要包括建造一個有機庫門的鋼結構停機庫（約80米×50米），安裝停機庫內的鋼結構，並提供所有在工場必要的防護油漆塗料，建造一組一層高的輔助工場，停機坪工程，外部鋪設道路，工地工程，水管，渠務設施以及機械，通風和空調及電力裝置。</p>','2025-05-31 04:27:26.012000','2025-07-07 08:01:04.972000',NULL,8,36,'zh-Hant-HK'),(21,'obsohs47sq88bd0yc7gdff4u','香港商用航空中心二号停机库扩建工程(称为三号停机库)','香港商用航空中心二号停机库扩建工程(称为三号停机库)','香港商用航空中心','2011 年 05 月 14 日 - 2012 年 05 月 31 日','<p>此工程是香港商用航空中心二号停机库的扩建工程，座落于二号停机库旁,称为三号停机库。新的三号停机库与现有的停机库相得益彰，提供足够的机库空间以满足香港飞机库不断增长的需求。</p><p>此工程主要包括建造一个有机库门的钢结构停机库（约80米×50米），安装停机库内的钢结构，并提供所有在工场必要的防护油漆涂料，建造一组一层高的辅助工场，停机坪工程，外部铺设道路，工地工程，水管，渠务设施以及机械，通风和空调及电力装置。</p>','2025-05-31 04:27:54.705000','2025-07-07 08:01:12.916000',NULL,8,36,'zh-CN'),(23,'pmsodcb4bmzeackf8ponnzvf','Proposed Extension to Hangar Two (also known as “Hangar Three”)','Proposed Extension to Hangar Two (also known as “Hangar Three”)','Hong Kong Business Aviation Centre, Ltd.','14 May 2011 - 31 May 2012','<p>The project is the extension of the existing Hangar Two operated by Hong Kong Business Aviation Centre, Ltd, namely as Hangar Three. The new third hangar aimed to complement the existing hangars in providing sufficient hangar spaces to meet the growing demand for aircraft hangars in Hong Kong.</p><p>Major works under the contract include the construction of an air-craft hangar building (approx. 80 m x 50m) with steel structure and metal cladding complete with hangar door, installation of the steel structure of the hangar building and providing all necessary protective painting at the fabrication yard and the construction of a group of one storey ancillary workshops, apron works, external paved roads, site works, plumbing, drainage installations and mechanical, ventilation and air conditioning and electrical installations.</p>','2025-05-31 04:28:45.658000','2025-07-07 08:01:15.157000',NULL,8,36,'en'),(25,'h2ryifurz6bqtvpn1ffl661w','Conversion of the Secondary Pool of the Lai Chi Kok Park Swimming Pool into an Indoor Heated Pool (Contract No. AL W316)','Conversion of the Secondary Pool of the Lai Chi Kok Park Swimming Pool into an Indoor Heated Pool','Architectural Services Department','01 February 2010 - 31 March 2012','<p>Hong Kong Government proposed to build an indoor heated swimming pool, which would have the effect of promoting swimming in winter and better health amongst the residents in the district, and thus enhancing the overall usage of the swimming pool.</p><p>The project includes the provision of a light cover and retractable sidewalls for the secondary pool; a new heating system to the secondary pool and a covered-walkway; demolition of the existing children&#x27;s fun pool and associated improvements to ventilation and hot water systems in changing room.</p>','2025-05-31 04:29:49.879000','2025-07-07 08:01:15.945000',NULL,8,36,'